body:

by Toxic_Tae

“What do you do, mister?” She asked shyly. This caught Hoseok’s attention as he watched the male give a faint smile. Hoseok’s heart pounded in his chest at that sight. He was even prettier with a smile. The stranger pulled off his sunglasses, looking down at the girl, that gentle smile still present.

“I make bad people go away.” The stranger spoke, pulling his sunglasses off to look down at the little girl fondly.
